    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司董事会选择派发 50% 股息，结束争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/petrobras-asks-investors-to-approve-50-payout-of-extra-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Petroleo Brasileiro SA 董事会决定从 2023 年起支付其潜在特别股息的 50%，解决了因总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 对这家国家控制的石油生产商施加过多影响而引发的一场震动巴西市场的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/petrobras-asks-investors-to-approve-50-payout-of-extra-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于销售放缓、库存增加，特斯拉在美国降价 2,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tesla-cuts-prices-by-2-000-as-sales-slow-inventories-swell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五晚间，特斯拉公司在美国将其最畅销的 Model Y、Model X 和 Model S 的价格下调了 2,000 美元，原因是第一季度销量令人失望推高了库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tesla-cuts-prices-by-2-000-as-sales-slow-inventories-swell</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆勒表示欧洲央行不应在六月后急于进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/ecb-shouldn-t-rush-further-rate-cuts-after-june-muller-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员马迪斯·穆勒 (Madis Muller) 表示，在 6 月份可能采取第一步之后，欧洲央行不应急于进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/ecb-shouldn-t-rush-further-rate-cuts-after-june-muller-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:38:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车田纳西工厂成立工会，为汽车联盟带来里程碑式的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/volkswagen-union-vote-uaw-and-shawn-fain-win-key-plant-in-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[田纳西州一家工厂的大众汽车公司员工投票加入汽车工人联合会，这是长期敌对的美国南部工会组织的一次里程碑式的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/volkswagen-union-vote-uaw-and-shawn-fain-win-key-plant-in-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:15:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷克托认为，如果比索跌至 59，菲律宾将面临延迟降息的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-recto-sees-rate-cut-delay-risk-if-peso-sinks-to-59</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾财政部长拉尔夫·雷克托警告说，如果比索兑美元汇率跌破 59 比索兑美元的历史低点，菲律宾可能会推迟降息，但这不会损害经济增长前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/philippines-recto-sees-rate-cut-delay-risk-if-peso-sinks-to-59</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
